  "A pharmaceutical chemist is analyzing aspirin (acetylsalicylic acid). The molecule contains both an ester group (C-O-C with a C=O) and a carboxylic acid group (COOH). She counts the sigma and pi bonds in the ester's C=O bond. How many sigma and pi bonds does a C=O double bond contain?": "",
